          article
            h2 Tolle <span id="billboard-gifts-gifts">Geschenke</span> unter <span id="billboard-gifts-price">15&thinsp;&euro;</span>
            ul
              li#billboard-gifts-link1
                = link_to '/libraries/8052' do
                  div
                  p Alle ansehen

        / Edle Tropfen
        .billboard#billboard-gourmet
          article
            h2 Edle<br>Tropfen
            = link_to '/users/mexican-tears?pk_campaign=bb5&pk_kwd=mexicantears' do
              | Klick mich,<br>ich bin <br>scharf<br>und<br>beliebt
